reviewText: Item arrived promptly and as described, couldn't be better!
I love this complicated and difficult Italian movie. It is difficult to watch and hard to understand at first.  But, I do love it.
This french-italian movie of the 80's is worth enough to be buyed, it has many famous actors and actresses of that time, as usual with european movies, is quite slow but it is interesting.

Beautiful film. Great actors, great story.
Una bella pelcula, espndida historia, un 'romance' inusual. Y una excelente reproduccin de la poca.
